data.text: #Update President #Trump His Objection to #NFL anthem boycott “has nothing to do with race,” is about “respect for our country (US)"
#Breaking President Trump has said more in a tweet about the protests by #NFL players during the national anthem https://t.co/JJehzSirsb
#Trump Sports fans shudd never condone players that do not stand proud for their National Anthem or their Country. #NFL shud change policy!
